"varia\" agenda. Provincially incorporated non-profits may have the ability to authorize the chair to reorder agenda items. It is also recommended to allow discussion on topics indicated by members.", "questions_this_excerpt_can_answer": "1. What are the key topics and entities involved in an annual general meeting (AGM) for organizations, as outlined in the document?\n2. In what circumstances can provincially incorporated non-profits authorize the chair to reorder agenda items during a general meeting, according to the document?\n3. How do organizations typically address funders' concerns or questions during an AGM, based on the information provided in the document?"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "c398db93-c6b8-4247-a9c3-c7431bf61392", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"page_label": "8", "file_name": "AGM-Legal-Info-Sheet-EN-2019.pdf", "file_path": "data\\dev\\docs\\AGM-Legal-Info-Sheet-EN-2019.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 432341, "creation_date": "2025-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2025-02-16"}, "hash": "96b41d6ec2e9e34c1a1c2e9ed69c15a6af0787162a0a8a8d006a47eea0601573", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "2": {"node_id": "732116b3-3008-46c2-ba14-44b7669ad01e", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {"page_label": "8", "file_name": "AGM-Legal-Info-Sheet-EN-2019.pdf", "file_path": "data\\dev\\docs\\AGM-Legal-Info-Sheet-EN-2019.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 432341, "creation_date": "2025-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2025-02-16"}, "hash": "965e5144e07c425c6e91346bf05a7000b4c08503411888b6d0e94532df6cbcc6", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "37c31f2a-8862-46a3-965f-85361fd0dc37", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "e76ad9d1743ea104c270f80a77a0639