rces available for administrators and members of associations, as well as a guide on the rights, duties, and responsibilities of administrators of non-profit organizations. The resources mentioned are primarily in French and can be borrowed from COCo's resource library or purchased from them. The section also mentions a toolbox on democratic governance for non-profit organizations in community action.", "questions_this_excerpt_can_answer": "1. What resources are available for administrators and members of non-profit associations in Quebec, and where can they be accessed?\n2. What guide provides information on the rights, duties, and responsibilities of administrators of non-profit organizations in Quebec?\n3. Where can non-profit organizations in the community and social economy sector find a toolbox on democratic governance specifically tailored to their needs?"}, "excluded_embed_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "excluded_llm_metadata_keys": ["file_name", "file_type", "file_size", "creation_date", "last_modified_date", "last_accessed_date"], "relationships": {"1": {"node_id": "369ede98-a66e-4554-94da-87bfc2409dda", "node_type": "4", "metadata": {"page_label": "19", "file_name": "AGM-Legal-Info-Sheet-EN-2019.pdf", "file_path": "data\\dev\\docs\\AGM-Legal-Info-Sheet-EN-2019.pdf", "file_type": "application/pdf", "file_size": 432341, "creation_date": "2025-02-16", "last_modified_date": "2025-02-16"}, "hash": "731644da201cadde801226c3ed52f05059e230f4593d96404e017e3859c83f2a", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}, "3": {"node_id": "892b1b73-f36b-4cb0-9a50-3938cd65eebf", "node_type": "1", "metadata": {}, "hash": "6693b762c6ba1c03f2f566f594a2f0d79e3f22840de864250d5a064f25ce86ce", "class_name": "RelatedNodeInfo"}}, "metadata_template": "{key}: {value}", "metadata_separator": "\n", "text": "19\nFurther resources & legal notices\nThe following resources provide detailed information on non-profit 